OL,3,CGrieving parents meet with Ofsted in
OL,4,Ccampaign to improve safety in nurseries
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney spoke with Genevieve's parents
OL,8,Fafter the Ofsted meeting.
OL,10,FThe parents of a baby who died at a
OL,11,Fnursery in Stockport have met with
OL,12,FOftsted in the latest stage of their
OL,13,Fcampaign to make early years settings
OL,14,Fsafer.
OL,16,FGenevieve Meehan died at nine-months-
OL,17,Fold after being left face down on a
OL,18,Fbeanbag at a nursery in Cheadle Hulme,
OL,19,FStockport, in May 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
