OL,3,CGrieving parents meet with Ofsted in
OL,4,Ccampaign to improve safety in nurseries
OL,6,FHer parents, Katie Wheeler and John
OL,7,FMeehan, travelled to the capital
OL,8,Fyesterday (Thursday) to once again
OL,9,Fpush for mandatory CCTV, and more
OL,10,Ffrequent inspections for Nurseries.
OL,12,FIn March 2026, the government outlined
OL,13,Fplans to tighten safety rules in the
OL,14,FEarly Years Foundation Stage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
