PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777665953
OL,3,CGrieving parents meet with Ofsted in
OL,4,Ccampaign to improve safety in nurseries
OL,6,FJohn says they were heartened
OL,7,Ffollowing the meeting: "We need to
OL,8,Fmake sure that Ofsted are going to be
OL,9,Freally robust - firstly in terms of
OL,10,Finspections and also the training of
OL,11,Finspectors. Ofsted gets it and they
OL,12,Fknow that they need to do that."
OL,14,FKatie says they also talked about the
OL,15,Finspection process: "There's such
OL,16,Foverwhelming evidence now that it's
OL,17,Fnot strong enough and Ofsted was
OL,18,Freally receptive."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777665953
OL,3,CGrieving parents meet with Ofsted in
OL,4,Ccampaign to improve safety in nurseries
OL,6,F"They've been working on changes and
OL,7,Fsay's they're really committed to
OL,8,Fstrengthening that process."
OL,10,FThe campaign also includes mandatory
OL,11,FCCTV in all settings and Katie says:
OL,12,F"There's a lot of support from parents
OL,13,Fincluding those whose children have
OL,14,Fbeen involved in very serious
OL,15,Fincidents of harm."
OL,17,F"We think everybody's voice together
OL,18,Fwill really push for change."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
