OL,3,CGrieving parents meet with Ofsted in
OL,4,Ccampaign to improve safety in nurseries
OL,6,FCCTV captured nine-month-old Genevieve
OL,7,Fstruggling to breath after being
OL,8,Ftightly swaddled and strapped face
OL,9,Fdown on a beanbag for more than an
OL,10,Fhour and a half at Tiny Toes nursery
OL,11,Fin, Stockport, in May 2022.
OL,13,FNursery deputy manager Kate Roughley,
OL,14,Fwas found guilty of manslaughter and
OL,15,Fjailed for 14 years in May 2024.
OL,17,FWhat are the three main points of the
OL,18,FCampaign for Gigi?
OL,20,FUse of CCTV
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
